        ],
        "Description": "This update upgrades gssproxy to version 0.8.3-alt1. \nSecurity Fix(es):\n\n * CVE-2020-12658: ** DISPUTED ** gssproxy (aka gss-proxy) before 0.8.3 does not unlock cond_mutex before pthread exit in gp_worker_main() in gp_workers.c. NOTE: An upstream comment states \"We are already on a shutdown path when running the code in question, so a DoS there doesn't make any sense, and there has been no additional information provided us (as upstream) to indicate why this would be a problem.\"",
